fb2.Name: Felix
fb2.Text: I can't believe she was silly enough to leave it among her unattended things!

fb2.Name: Felix
fb2.Text: Rather careless of a belle like her.

fb2.Name: Felix
fb2.Text: Without this, she won't be able to...

fb2.Name: Felix
fb2.Text: ... yes, yes. It's all coming together. She won't have a choice.
